1. People love saying "getting a gf won't make you happier and less depressed".

It absolutely will and should be a major goal of the majority of people here. People are meant to be together.

2. Only contrary idiots make fun of people for being nostalgic about the 50s/60s. You KNOW they were a happier and more wholesome time.

Yeah, they did lead to today - but so did the Medieval era.
3. Religious infighting and owning between protestant, Catholics and Orthodox is idiocy. Act like normal men for once.
4. Young people today wishing to live away from their famililes is understandable and not something unnatural (but also not something good)

5. Making fun of people for "fornicating" is too overdone. Yes, it is sinful behaviour - but making fun of random twitter chicks for sleeping with random men is not going to help them, and it is not going to help your soul. If you care so much, say a prayer for them or smth
6. Powerlifting, as I have said many times, is foolishness. Do bodybuilding instead. You are not going to be using your strength gains anyways.
7. University/college is good if you study something marketable. Trade jobs are boring and might ruin your health.
8. YOU have the potential to become a saint. Reflect on this thought.
9. If you believe there are more than two ideologies, you have more studying to do.

10. and 11. Birds are better than cats and dogs. Pineapple is good on pizza.

13. Not reading "popular" authors in this sphere like Ted. K or Evola is stupid. They are still incredibly niche anyways.
14. Don't focus too much on your diet or optimization of routine. It is not good or healthy. Skip a workout occasionally, it will not hurt your progress.

16. Paganism, to me, is not bad, but a bit silly. I understand why it is attractive though.
17. Logo actually looks pretty ok lmao
18. Don't focus on your legs/squat. Just don't. I'm saying it for your own good.

21. I do not enjoy reading poetry.
22. Americans have plenty reasons to be patriotic and an interesting history.
23. The clown meme has been ultra cringe from the star, I have no fucking idea how some of you even found it funny in the first place
24. Space is kinda cool. Science, contrary to what some say, is freaking awesome. Science was never meant to be what science now is though.
25. Never use headphones or earbuds. Just don't.
26. Metal is trash. People obsessed with metal often have psychological problems. It's overstimulating. Do not listen to metal too often.
27. Do not watch horror movies more than once every few months. Maybe Halloween is an exception. Same case as metal.
28. Deadlifts are overrated.
29. Deadlifts should only be done without chalk or other bullshit, with a double overhand grip. Do not go above 4 plates.
30. Some modern / "post-modern" art is incredibly beautiful and interesting. You just don't understand it.
31. Neofolk is meh
32. Being offensive on purpose is never good. Act like normal people.
